      "description": "Get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for a dedicated mechanic or someone looking for a valuable source of parts. While it is currently in poor condition and will require some significant work to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic opportunity to build something from the ground up at an affordable entry point!",
