    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been preserved with the utmost care. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and factory-fresh, showing no signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, the car performs exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line, with every feature, button, and electronic system functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained example that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by authorized technicians.",
      "price": 49500.0,
