    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber, maintained to the most exacting standards. This vehicle exhibits an immaculate aesthetic and mechanical profile, representing the definitive pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior appointments, every detail reflects a legacy of uncompromising care and preservation. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly superlative condition, offering a driving experience that remains indistinguishable from its original state.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
